==English==

===Pronunciation===
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /'/
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /'bεnd/

===Verb===
{{irregverb|bend|[[bends]]|[[bent]]|[[bent]]|[[bending]]}}
====Transitive====
# To cause (something) to change its shape into a [[curve]], by [[physical]] [[force]], [[chemical]] action, or any other means.
# (''nautical'') To [[join]] one [[rope]] to another, or to an object
#: ''Bend the sail to the yard.''
# (''nautical'') To [[swing]] the [[body]] when [[rowing]]
# (''music'') To smoothly change the pitch of a note.
#: ''You should bend the G sligthly sharp in the next measure.''

