=== Noun ===
'''bend''' (plural: '''[[bends]]''')

# A [[curve]].
#: ''There's a sharp bend in the road ahead.''
# (''nautical'') A [[knot]] used to join two [[rope]]s, or to tie a rope onto something.
#*Note: In naval parlance, a knot involves splicing the strands of a rope.
# (''plural, medicine, diving'') A severe condition caused by excessively quick decompression, causing bubbles of [[nitrogen]] to form in the [[blood]], [[decompression sickness]].
#: ''A diver who stays deep for too long must ascend very slowly in order to prevent the bends.''

